snippet.title: God of Rock – Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Battle to the beat! Join the universe’s greatest clash for musical supremacy in this rhythm-fighting game hybrid. Choose from a dozen unique fighters, each with their own design, mechanics, and harmonic attacks, and master 48 original rock tracks. Do you have what it takes to become the God of Rock champion? God of Rock is available to purchase now at https://www.xbox.com/games/store/god-of-rock/9pkq1q2qgrj5
